high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and begin walking across the room, hang another left and walk up to the yellow vase on the glass table.
Pick up the yellow vase that is just below the white plate on the glass table.
Turn right and walk around the couch over to the cardboard box that is on the couch seat.
Place the yellow vase inside the cardboard box.
Pick up the cardboard box with the yellow vase inside of it.
Turn right and begin walking to the wall, the hang a left and walk back over to the glass table.
Place the cardboard box with the yellow vase inside of it on the end of the glass table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a yellow vase inside of it on the glass table.

high_descs: Walk behind the couch that is to the right and stop at the table to the right in front of the yellow bowl.
Pick up the yellow bowl from the edge of the table.
Turn right, walk to the front of the couch, and stop ion front of the box.
Put the yellow bowl inside of the box that's on the couch.
Pick the box up from the couch.
Walk behind the couch and turn to face the table.
Put the box down on the table behind the envelope closest to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a yellow bowl in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn left, then go straight then turn around the back of the couch, then turn right to face the dining table.
Pick up the yellow vase on the table, in front of the plate.
Turn right, go around the couch, then turn right to face the box on the couch.
Place the vase in the box on the couch.
Pick up the box with the vase in it.
Go around the couch, then turn right to face the dining table.
Put the box on the table, behind the right most newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put a vase in a box on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table to where the yellow vase is.
Pick up the yellow vase that is on the table.
With the vase in hand go to the couch where the box is on the couch.
Put the vase in the box.
Pick up the box with the vase in it.
With the vase with the box in go to the table where the grey bowl is.
On the table put the box to the right of the bowl behind the card that is the one all the way to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put vase in box to put on table.
